@startuml completeness-validation-activity
title AKDB Agent-Authoring - Completeness Validation (spec_validate)
start
:Load archetype contract from archetype_requirements.yml;
note right: required_diagrams + file_map + blocking, by archetype (plugin/function/rule)
:Collect spec_realizes_uml links -> realized diagrams;
:Collect element_maps_to_file links for core (component-level) elements;
if (all required_diagrams satisfied?) then (no)
  :add missing_required_diagrams;
else (yes)
endif
:Resolve each file-map target_ref against source_areas / repo;
if (every target resolves?) then (no)
  :add unresolved_file_map;
else (yes)
endif
if (every core element covered by a file-map?) then (no)
  :add uncovered_elements (warning);
else (yes)
endif
:Check links point at existing items;
if (dangling refs?) then (yes)
  :add dangling_refs;
else (no)
endif
:Write findings to consistency_findings;
if (any blocking category non-empty?) then (yes)
  :Refuse draft -> ready;
  stop
else (no)
  :Allow draft -> ready;
  stop
endif
@enduml
